{"type":null,"faqId":40553,"title":"如何用Huawei HiLink远程管理家里的路由器？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.p1{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.15763889in;margin-left:0.15763889in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:0.31527779in;margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;color:#00a0e9;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4861111in;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.36805555in;}\n.s4{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>只要您的手机有网络，就能通过华为账号（已和路由器绑定）登录Huawei HiLink，华为云功能将使您不在家也能远程管理家里的路由器。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">远程管理前，请做以下准备工作</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">&gt;  </span><span>您需要有一个华为账号。如果还没有，可以先在华为官网上注册，或稍后在华为账号绑定页面注册。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">&gt;  </span><span>首次使用时，您需要在路由器的Wi-Fi环境下，将华为账号与路由器绑定。绑定方法如下：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>手机连接路由器的Wi-Fi。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>打开Huawei HiLink。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>点击右上角设置图标 </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137628\" style=\"width:0.19791667in;height:0.19791667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>点击“</span><span class=\"s4\">账户 &gt; 华为账号</span><span>”，根据页面信息绑定已有的华为账号或新注册一个账号后绑定。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137629\" style=\"width:5.2743053in;height:3.9361112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">您可按照以下步骤进行远程管理</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>打开Huawei HiLink。无论您在何处，只要手机可以上网即可。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>点击首页左上角的远程登录图标 </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137630\" style=\"width:0.16041666in;height:0.15625in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s3\">1  </span><span>点击“</span><span class=\"s4\">远程登录</span><span>”并使用之前绑定的华为账号登录。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=137631\" style=\"width:2.4291666in;height:3.9402778in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>使用华为账号登录成功后，您就可以像在家一样，管理家里的路由器了。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5900","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1441768547000,"seriesProductName":"WS832-10","visitedTimes":59,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}